		<!-- Blog post -->
		<div class="blog-item">
			<img src="~/img/blog/22.jpg" alt="">
			<div class="blog-date">April 14, 2019</div>
			<h3>玫瑰墓樂團 用生命來寫歌 用音樂來說故事</h3>
			<div class="blog-meta">by <a href="">Alan Smith</a> in <a href="">Music</a></div>
			<p>
